APEX CODE TO CONVERT INR TO USD
======================================================================

public class basic 
{
    public static void base()
    {
        decimal inr = 10000;
        decimal usd;
        usd = inr/75;
        system.debug('INR TO USD : ' +usd);
    }

}

======================================================================

TO EXECUTE USE THE FOLLOWING COMMAND

basic.base();

======================================================================
